multispeech (2.7.0jessie1) jessie; urgency=low

  * Introduced sync and async audio stream operation strategies.
  * Implemented native PulseAudio API support.
  * Discarded spurious messages on stderr in non-verbose mode.
  * Revised language detection patterns.
  * Fixed naming of audio devices.
  * Added an option to get list of all available devices on the system.
  * Fixed package related info.
  * Removed outdated Orca cooperation hints.

